          "reviewBody": "After two years of COVID gap kids are participating in Science expo 2022.well organised by Sri Chaitanya Techno School  Ramapuram branch. Projects was done in school not in home so that students got good knowledge while doing in school. Students explained the demo  both in English and Tamil so that parents and grandparents can understand. Demo done by students are neat, clean and explained in clear tone. Thanks to the Dean, Principal, Teachers giving an opportunity to our kids and thanks to other staff members of Sri Chaitanya Techno School Ramapuram",
