          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi ,I am P.Duriya mother. My daughter is studying in IK 1  in Sri chaitaniya techno school Ramapuram chennai.here teaching is super.\n\nMrs.meharunisha was the class  teacher for my daughter.She got a nice & dedicative  class teacher (Mrs.meharunisha ) mam, she is so kind and her session is so interactive  for the kids.\n\n( Sri chaitanya techno school ramapuram chennai) the management has well experience teachers, and teaching methods are very good.\n\nMy daughter was very happy while she receives the All Round five star performer award.\n\nThis moment to thank the principal, coordinator and the teacher's.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
