          },
          "reviewBody": "So what.. says sri chaitanya techno school...though we suffer in the pandemic situation. They are giving such a Quality of education to all of their children with new techniques and efforts of highly skilled teachers are appreciable. They made the online classes as live school...💐💐💐All the very best for all of you for....Srichaitanya techno school Management, principal mam and beloved teachers who deserves and made possible  to reach education to our doorsteps. Thank you...N.Balu, F/o Johith Advai Ik2 and Mahith Advai 3B, Ramapuram campus.",
